<div class="full-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center justify-content-center my-3">
      <h1>
        Thank you
        <strong style="color: orange"><%= @business.user.first_name %></strong>
        <strong style="color: orange"><%= @business.user.last_name %></strong>
        for partnering with us!
      </h1>
      <p>Congratulations! Your company profile has been successfully created and you can now submit your first vehicles.</p><br>
      <p>If you don't see your vehicles immediately on our platform, please don't worry.</p><br>
      <p>Our team performs regular checks to ensure that our partners comply with our security and quality guidelines.</p><br>
      <p><strong>Here are your company details:</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="booking-card">
      <ul>
        <li>Organisation Name: <strong style="color: orange"><%= @business.organisation_name %></strong>.</li>
        <li>Tax Number: <strong style="color: orange"><%= @business.tax_number %></strong>.</li>
        <li>Tax Number: <strong style="color: orange"><%= @business.address %></strong>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center justify-content-center my-3">
      <p>We are excited to collaborate with you and look forward to serving our customers together!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <p><%= link_to "Submit first vehicle", new_vehicle_path %></p>
  </div>
</div>
